01:09:02,407 --> 01:09:05,574
<i>There's something wrong with her.</i>

567
01:09:05,744 --> 01:09:11,332
<i>If you're a Wormwood, it's time
you started acting like one!</i>

568
01:10:22,700 --> 01:10:28,204
<i>That was one of my favorites,
played for all you pretty ones.</i>

569
01:10:28,372 --> 01:10:29,932
<i>Playing music to make you smile...</i>

570
01:10:29,933 --> 01:10:31,492
