591
01:13:05,095 --> 01:13:06,446
Chew your food!

592
01:13:11,751 --> 01:13:15,915
<i>Having power isn't as important
as what you do with it.</i>

593
01:13:16,089 --> 01:13:21,629
<i>And what Matilda had in mind
was nothing short of heroic.</i>

594
01:14:44,431 --> 01:14:47,635
Come on!

