- Guam?

671
01:29:08,918 --> 01:29:12,703
- Daddy's out of business.
- I don't want to!

672
01:29:12,881 --> 01:29:17,838
- We're taking a permanent vacation!
- We have to hurry to the airport.

673
01:29:18,010 --> 01:29:22,839
